Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.82,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,At the Hyatt Regency, the\Ndeadly change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.62,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,looked like a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The walkway design used\None continuous hangar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,rod from roof to fourth\Nfloor to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.65,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In shop drawings, it\Nbecame two shorter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.24,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,rods, easier to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the load path changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.16,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The fourth floor\Nconnection now carried both
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,walkways, not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.77,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The load essentially\Ndoubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,NBS later found the\Noriginal design was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.60,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,already weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:33.27,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The revision left roughly\None-third of code-expected
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:34.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,On July 17, 1981, two\Nwalkways collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:41.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,during a crowded dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.76,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Official records count 113\Ndead and 186
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:47.43,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,This was not a shop\Ndetail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.21,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was a structural\Nredesign.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.26,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Every handoff treated it\Nlike paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.96,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
